## 7. SUBMISSION CHECKLIST

To submit this proposal on Upwork:

1. Copy the cover letter text from cover-letter.md into the Upwork proposal field.
   The letter is Upwork-paste-ready: markdown bold (**...**) may need conversion to
   plain text if Upwork's input strips markdown. Test paste in preview mode.

2. Attach or link the one-pager:
   Option A (recommended): paste the URL if one-pager is published to the site.
   Option B: export one-pager.html to PDF and attach as PDF to the Upwork proposal.

3. Attach deck.pptx if Upwork allows file attachments (or export to PDF first).

4. The demo link https://michaelwegter.com/work-samples/full-stack-developer-python-fastapi
   appears in the cover letter body (paragraph 2). Confirm it loads in a browser
   before submitting.

5. Confirm the site has been deployed (push to main triggers GH Pages deploy).
   The demo URL will 404 until the site build propagates (~1-2 minutes post-push).

